    <item>
      <title>Social Sharing Shortcodes</title>
      <link>http://ivan.fraixed.es/hugo-resources/social-sharing/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Dec 2015 08:20:31 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://ivan.fraixed.es/hugo-resources/social-sharing/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;In this page you can see the available social sharing shortcodes showing a live example and code sample.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;facebook-share-button:89e43e7b944c916f0e4ced1926fc907b&#34;&gt;Facebook share button&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Render a Facebook share button, like 
&lt;div id=&#34;fb-root&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script&gt;(function(d, s, id) {
  var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];
  if (d.getElementById(id)) return;
  js = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;
  js.src = &#34;//connect.facebook.net/en_US/all.js#xfbml=1&#34;;
  fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);
}(document, &#39;script&#39;, &#39;facebook-jssdk&#39;));&lt;/script&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;fb-share-button&#34; data-href=&#34;example.com&#34;data-layout=&#34;button_count&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It has only one positional parameter and is optional; the default is &lt;code&gt;page URL&lt;/code&gt; value.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #f8f8f8&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;No&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;parameter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;so&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;page&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;will&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;be&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;used&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;facebook&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;share&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Using&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;passed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;parameter&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;facebook&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;share&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;http://example.com&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 id=&#34;pinterest-follow-button:89e43e7b944c916f0e4ced1926fc907b&#34;&gt;Pinterest follow button&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Render a Pinterest follow button, like 
  &lt;a data-pin-do=&#34;buttonFollow&#34; href=&#34;https://www.pinterest.com/ifraixedes/&#34;&gt;Ivan Fraixedes&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;script async defer src=&#34;//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinit.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It has several named parameters:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;username: The username to follow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;fullname (optional): The text to use inside the button; it uses &amp;ldquo;username&amp;rdquo; parameters by default.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Optionally you can also used with the single required parameter (&lt;code&gt;username&lt;/code&gt;) as a positional parameter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #f8f8f8&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Using&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;only&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;username&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinterest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;follow&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;username&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;ifraixedes&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Using&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;passed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;parameter&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinterest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;follow&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;username&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;golang&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;fullname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;Go&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Using&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;it&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;positional&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;single&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;username&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;required&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;parameter&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinterest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;follow&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;golang&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 id=&#34;pinterest-pin-it-button:89e43e7b944c916f0e4ced1926fc907b&#34;&gt;Pinterest pin it button&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Render a Pinterest pin it button, like 
  &lt;a data-pin-do=&#34;buttonPin&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3a%2f%2fivan.fraixed.es%2fhugo-resources%2fsocial-sharing%2f&amp;media=https%3a%2f%2fgohugo.io%2fimg%2fhugo.png&amp;description=Social%20Sharing%20Shortcodes -- Hugo%20Resources&#34; data-pin-color=&#34;red&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;script async defer src=&#34;//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinit.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It has several named parameters:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;media: The absolute URL to the image to pin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;url (optional): The absolute URL to pages which contains the image to pin. Default is &lt;code&gt;page URL&lt;/code&gt; value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;large (optional): Use a large button. Default is &lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;description (optional): The description for the image to pin. Default to string composed by &lt;code&gt;page title - site title&lt;/code&gt; if they aren&amp;rsquo;t equal otherwise &lt;code&gt;page title&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;color (optional): The color of the button that Pinterest has available. Default to &lt;code&gt;red&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Optionally you can also used with the single required parameter (&lt;code&gt;media&lt;/code&gt;) as a positional parameter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #f8f8f8&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Using&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;lage&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;button&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;an&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;description&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinterest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;media&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;https://gohugo.io/img/hugo.png&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;large&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;true&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;This an example of a hugo shortcode for Pinterest Pin Button&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Changing&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinterest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;media&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;https://gohugo.io/img/hugo.png&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;grey&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Using&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;it&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;positional&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;single&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;media&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;required&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;parameter&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinterest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;pinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;https://gohugo.io/img/hugo.png&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;twitter-follow-button:89e43e7b944c916f0e4ced1926fc907b&#34;&gt;Twitter follow button&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Render a Twitter button, like 
  &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/brody_berson&#34; class=&#34;twitter-follow-button&#34; data-show-count=&#34;true&#34; data-show-screen-name=&#34;true&#34; data-size=&#34;large&#34;&gt;Follow @brody_berson&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;script&gt;!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],p=/^http:/.test(d.location)?&#39;http&#39;:&#39;https&#39;;if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src=p+&#39;://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js&#39;;fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document, &#39;script&#39;, &#39;twitter-wjs&#39;);&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It has several named parameters:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;username: The username to follow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;show-count (optional): Number of followers label. Set to &amp;ldquo;true&amp;rdquo; it&amp;rsquo;s shown otherwise &lt;strong&gt;not shown&lt;/strong&gt;. Default not shown.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;show-name (optional): Show username in the button. Set to &amp;ldquo;true&amp;rdquo; it&amp;rsquo;s shown otherwise &lt;strong&gt;not shown&lt;/strong&gt;. Default not shown.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;large (optional): Show large button. Set to &amp;ldquo;true&amp;rdquo; show in large, otherwise in normal size.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Optionally you can also used with the single required parameter (&lt;code&gt;username&lt;/code&gt;) as a positional parameter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #f8f8f8&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;Twitter&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;large&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;button&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;showing&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;username&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000&#34;&gt;followers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ce5c00; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
